{"tid":846178,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士司機被捕後不治　cctv見警疑拳打事主　警拒回答：合理最低武力","createTime":"2018-10-03T08:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T10:56:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5605b48e24a1cde631fe1bc2a0f97f16d4c80153","tid":846178,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181003/s00001/34f5ad9a9f674551f0c7db7f48c4b102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181003%2Fs00001%2F34f5ad9a9f674551f0c7db7f48c4b102.jpg&h=294faf04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員馬振康。（劉焌陶攝）<br />\n<br />\n警方於6年前在西隧收費亭，拘捕一名疑因車費問題與乘客爭執動武之的士司機。警員制服司機及押上警車期間，疑使用過分武力致司機出現頸椎移位，全身癱瘓臥牀近一個月後因肺炎不治。死因庭今繼續研訊。閉路電視片段顯示，負責將事主搬上警車的警員疑似有拳打的動作，警員拒絕回答家屬代表律師提問他是否有打過事主，強調他是使用合理的最低武力。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：被捕的士司機全身癱瘓留醫一個月不治 閉路電視片段見警員箍頸扯事主上車<br />\n<br />\n代表家屬的資深大律師蘇朗年，向拘捕事主陳輝旺的警員馬振康指出，警員向事主宣布拘捕後，從西隧的閉路電視片段可見，事主並沒有掙扎和反抗，但警員仍將事主壓在地上，鎖上手銬。馬反指，閉路電視鏡頭會移動，剛好事主正在反抗約半分鐘時間，鏡頭未有拍下。<br />\n<br />\n蘇朗年指，片段可見他將事主搬上警車時，右手臂疑似有拳打的動作，直問馬究竟在做什麼，馬回應他不願回答，強調當時使用的武力合理，是以最低武力控制事主，而當事主受控後，他就停止。蘇朗年直接向馬指出，即使他不願回答問題，但片中明顯可見他在拳打事主，馬不同意。<br />\n<br />\n馬解釋他判斷當場不需要使用「4人搬離法」，即由4名人員分別抬起反抗人士的雙手和雙腳，因當時已為事主鎖上手銬，而把事主整個身體凌空抬起的風險太大。代表警務處和消防處的大律師提問下，馬同意因為現場環境千變萬化，教官曾言「戰場無絕對」，因此他在決定如何搬動疑犯時都會靈活處理，並指現場不是人手不足。<br />\n<br />\n研訊午續。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181003/s00001/1538546262583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181003%2Fs00001%2F1538546262583&d=y20W634u0Ambr8VjUlsI4YsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=8457a39b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181003%2Fs00001%2F1538546262583&h=d78b5d40\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181003/s00001/1538546262583</a>"},{"pid":"025a03491663dc310e0c10cd6cde4ba6d74987b5","tid":846178,"uid":61748,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c452e58a8d816a8f9ab6ddfae04d4582326f101","tid":846178,"uid":70439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"Dc9(死亡）vs 警犬"},{"pid":"d642e1673d322b6fd7bbcb130e7a95afb049b8cd","tid":846178,"uid":26752,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5c452e58a8d816a8f9ab6ddfae04d4582326f101","tid":846178,"uid":70439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"Dc9(死亡）vs 警犬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"DC9死亡+警犬入獄=best ending <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e723516cc9a43a7b87c931d4bbf0156df7cc85ae","tid":846178,"uid":6674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291f50845078a31ab579ddedbabb90e1a9a8962e","tid":846178,"uid":70439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d642e1673d322b6fd7bbcb130e7a95afb049b8cd","tid":846178,"uid":26752,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5c452e58a8d816a8f9ab6ddfae04d4582326f101","tid":846178,"uid":70439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"Dc9(死亡）vs 警犬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"DC9死亡+警犬入獄=best ending <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:23:21.000Z","msg":"彩蛋係警犬入到去俾其他罪犯屌屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b434ecfee46772a7c8c87b0dd5a65b1a672fd7a6","tid":846178,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"291f50845078a31ab579ddedbabb90e1a9a8962e","tid":846178,"uid":70439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d642e1673d322b6fd7bbcb130e7a95afb049b8cd","ti